modName: High Definition Canvas Undergarments - UNP UNPB and UNP Skinny versions
summary: Loose canvas texture, can see through the \\\"holes\\\" - not solid. Working alpha channel.
descriptionHtml:
I am taking private requests again...

=== High Definition Canvas Undergarments ===
Requires at least: Skyrim, UNP/UNPB
Version: 0.4b

I disliked the texture that Dimon99 had included so I started over from scratch and redid it. Thank you for downloading one of my custom undergarment texture. I have created high definition (2048x2048) textures for UNP and UNPB undergarments.

== Description ==
This is a super high quality canvas bikini texture for UNP undergarments. It has a working alpha channel so you can see through the loose mesh, so it is kind of transparent.  This will change the stock \"lacey\" undergarments into a canvas bikini style undergarments. Enjoy.

== Installation ==
Place the \'textures\' and \'meshes\' folder into your Skyrim/Data folder and merge/overwrite if necessary or install via NMM.

== Changelog ==
0.4b - First public release
